                </p>

                <h1 style="margin:0 0 16px 0; text-align:center; font-size:36px; line-height:1.2;">
                  October in Motion
                </h1>

                <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0; text-align:center; font-size:22px;">
                  Dreamforce, SF security changes, and Serpent 2.5 updates you should not miss
                </p>

                <p style="margin:0 0 32px 0; text-align:center; font-size:14px; color:#666666;">
                  Released: October 2025 | Version 2.5.0
                </p>

                <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0; text-align:center; font-size:20px; font-weight:bold;">
                  Big news this month: we are hitting the road, sharing critical security updates, and shipping a major Serpent release.
                </p>

                <p style="margin:0 0 24px 0; text-align:center;">
                  From Dreamforce to new platform changes, here is everything you need to know.
                </p>

                <h2 style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:26px;">Salesforce Updates and News</h2>

                <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="margin:0 0 24px 0; border:1px solid #d9d9d9; background-color:#ffffff;">
                  
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:20px;">
                        <h3 style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:24px;">Key Changes to Connected App Security</h3>
                        <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">
                          Salesforce introduced critical changes that could impact your org if not addressed by admins.
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">
                          We have detailed what changed and how to stay ahead:
                          <a href="https://tekunda.com/blog/Major-Changes-to-Salesforce-Connected-App-Security%2C-Is-Your-Org-Ready%3F">Read the full breakdown</a>
                        </p>
                        <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:20px;">
                          <li>Blocked access to uninstalled Connected Apps</li>
                          <li>Removed OAuth 2.0 Device Flow from Data Loader</li>
                          <li>New permission: Approve Uninstalled Connected Apps</li>
                        </ul>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  
                </table>

                <h2 style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:26px;">Where We Will Be</h2>

                <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="margin:0 0 24px 0; border:1px solid #d9d9d9; background-color:#ffffff;">
                  
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:20px;">
                        <h3 style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:24px;">Dreamforce 2025</h3>
                        <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">
                          This week, we are heading to Dreamforce 2025.
                        </p>
                        <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:20px;">
                          <li>October 14-16 in San Francisco</li>
                          <li><a href="https://tekunda.com/serpent#contact">Let us connect</a>, share ideas, and maybe grab a coffee</li>
                          <li>See you at Dreamforce</li>
                        </ul>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  
                </table>

                <h2 style="margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:26px;">What Is New in Serpent 2.5</h2>

                <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="margin:0 0 20px 0; border:1px solid #d9d9d9; background-color:#ffffff;">
                  
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:20px;">
                        <h3 style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:22px;">Dark Mode Is Here</h3>
                        <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">Designed for comfort, styled for clarity.</p>
                        <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:20px;">
                          <li>Dark Mode is now available across the platform</li>
                          <li>Follows your system settings, or set it permanently</li>
                          <li>Every page, chart, and detail is refined for dark mode</li>
                        </ul>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  
                </table>

                <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="margin:0 0 20px 0; border:1px solid #d9d9d9; background-color:#ffffff;">
                  
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:20px;">
                        <h3 style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:22px;">Enterprise Permissions, Made Easy</h3>
                        <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">Secure, scalable, and built for real teams.</p>
                        <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:20px;">
                          <li>Assign full or project-specific access as needed</li>
                          <li>Visibility into roles and access, always up to date</li>
                          <li>Built for enterprises needing more flexibility and control</li>
                        </ul>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  
                </table>

                <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="margin:0 0 20px 0; border:1px solid #d9d9d9; background-color:#ffffff;">
                  
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:20px;">
                        <h3 style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:22px;">Insights That Move With You</h3>
                        <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">Your work, visualised in real time.</p>
                        <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:20px;">
                          <li>The new Analytics Dashboard surfaces deployment activity and success rates</li>
                          <li>Monitor tasks and release flows across all projects</li>
                          <li>Spot trends and guide decisions with data</li>
                        </ul>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  
                </table>

                <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="margin:0 0 32px 0; border:1px solid #d9d9d9; background-color:#ffffff;">
                  
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:20px;">
                        <h3 style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:22px;">Smarter Logs and Release Details</h3>
                        <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">See issues and solve them faster.</p>
                        <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:20px;">
                          <li>Action logs and release history now show clear, contextual error messages</li>
                          <li>Redesigned layouts help you debug faster with less effort</li>
                          <li>Instant clarity on what happened</li>
                        </ul>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  
                </table>

                <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="margin:0 0 32px 0; background-color:#1d9aa5;">
                  
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:24px; text-align:center; color:#ffffff;">
                        <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:20px; font-weight:bold;">
                          TL;DR? Here is what is happening this month:
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">
                          Major changes to Salesforce Connected App Security
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">
                          We are at Dreamforce 2025, October 14-16 in San Francisco
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;">
                          Serpent 2.5 is live with Dark Mode, refined navigation, enterprise permissions, and actionable analytics
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0;">
                          All designed to keep you moving securely, clearly, and at scale.
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin:0;">
